{"tid":799784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍灣商貿區食店 性價比高選擇","createTime":"2018-08-30T10:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T06:24:36.000Z","uid":82640,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"469194bfb96ea90f6a938e9d08edeee1e4a77348","tid":799784,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"九龍灣商貿區實在少吸引人嘅餐廳#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />_2#<br />\n物價高到以為自己去咗中環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家平時食飯有咩性價比高選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己拋磚引玉咁掉幾間食店先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好食唔係燥就係菜式太常見，唔啱日日食<br />\n1. <strong>信和食堂</strong>：隱世中菜，高水準蒸炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/na4JYyDFGBE2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2Fna4JYyDFGBE2&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e05bbd2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/na4JYyDFGBE2</a><br />\n2. <strong>企業廣場飯堂</strong>：講真比起一般茶記貴少少，但配料多好多煮得好食好多（熱氣好多）<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/6uDkmjDXU832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F6uDkmjDXU832&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1599db75\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/6uDkmjDXU832</a><br />\n<br />\n偏貴都算，最撚麻煩係呢2間都真係好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlunch時間真係企20分鐘都未必有得食#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#<br />\n1. <strong>茶室</strong>：5x蚊唔算貴，用料有保證；最煩係勁多人排隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/eRpsAqKKBBD2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FeRpsAqKKBBD2&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2301e003\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/eRpsAqKKBBD2</a><br />\n2. <strong>IKEA餐廳</strong>：有蟲都長期爆場，問心好難有類近性價比餐廳<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/yynnWgfQMmn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FyynnWgfQMmn&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f6a7518a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/yynnWgfQMmn</a><br />\n<br />\n白痴負評選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. <strong>美味園</strong>：港式茶記黎講除咗平同有果汁揀，碟頭真係hea到不能形容<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/bPcBa5yimg12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FbPcBa5yimg12&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e68d0fcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/bPcBa5yimg12</a><br />\n2. <strong>Casa Luca</strong>：空氣包都算仲要係紙皮咁硬，大量港女打卡力撐<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/VY4DG9B38s22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FVY4DG9B38s22&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=fefb6d82\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/VY4DG9B38s22</a>"},{"pid":"4ba514fd114982c707cb13d48952b9a2f21b61a0","tid":799784,"uid":143125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"零碳斜對面 OK隨離上一層禮記 兩餸/三餸飯 都幾抵食 外賣仲平少少"},{"pid":"a61df18344705c4b6df5e9820398636317c16dbf","tid":799784,"uid":143125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>零碳斜對面 OK<span style=\"color: red;\">隨</span>離上一層禮記 兩餸/三餸飯 都幾抵食 外賣仲平少少</blockquote><br />\n隔離"},{"pid":"15f9bab3d86c5afbb4eca39dca99a058786a118f","tid":799784,"uid":25002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10259af7e7e3b4881859561e4468a46093ef7d6e","tid":799784,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15f9bab3d86c5afbb4eca39dca99a058786a118f","tid":799784,"uid":25002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"好貴喎"},{"pid":"8ad3416ee50730356d619dd788764bb232757844","tid":799784,"uid":23560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:25:56.000Z","msg":"百麵棧好食<br />\nEmax間品味都算唔差<br />\n<br />\n唔怕遠啟業正記都好食"},{"pid":"24732cb755f64a1a88aa34965f3611c7bba1d646","tid":799784,"uid":86015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c766e247fda5a0910abae668356e0f2c1760381","tid":799784,"uid":29447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"呢排瘋狂叫plum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d6f4cfda25e404b6bbb5bb50bfd2d1831842c7","tid":799784,"uid":36670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24732cb755f64a1a88aa34965f3611c7bba1d646","tid":799784,"uid":86015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"Details? 街外人都食得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有間唔錯，叫D&amp;A House<br />\n份量多，成2-3大塊扒咁上<br />\n但隔音差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n100%耳朵受罪<br />\n<br />\n其次就企業廣場3，過海的士站隔離有間小食店都唔錯<br />\n佢主打三文治同鮮搾果汁，都幾平<br />\n但我食開佢36蚊一個飯，幾抵屌<br />\n<br />\n其他就禮記果d，係果頭做開都識架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757a6c21839e691b1fa088bff15126d642c8ccb6","tid":799784,"uid":171668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime